</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/2_54b69dff-3da7-4a0f-908f-33a251bde115.png?v=1708696016" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/2_54b69dff-3da7-4a0f-908f-33a251bde115.png?v=1708696016 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/2_54b69dff-3da7-4a0f-908f-33a251bde115_1500x.png?v=1708696016 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/2_54b69dff-3da7-4a0f-908f-33a251bde115_1000x.png?v=1708696016 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/2_54b69dff-3da7-4a0f-908f-33a251bde115_500x.png?v=1708696016 320w" width="1613" height="1075" alt="Discover the Future of Learning: Why ComplyPlus LMS is Leading the Way - Dr Richard Dune - " title="Discover the Future of Learning: Why ComplyPlus LMS is Leading the Way - Dr Richard Dune - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-132_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-133_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by traimakivan via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-135_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Unlike traditional intelligence, business intelligence is not solely acquired through formal education or training. It often sprouts in the fertile grounds of everyday life, manifesting in behaviours and inclinations observed from childhood through adolescence. These early signs, when nurtured, can bloom into formidable business acumen.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-137_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-138_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-139_">Childhood - The playground of business skills
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_54e2a8a6-06af-4d5b-b812-a07814deacd3.png?v=1708696015" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_54e2a8a6-06af-4d5b-b812-a07814deacd3.png?v=1708696015 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_54e2a8a6-06af-4d5b-b812-a07814deacd3_1000x.png?v=1708696015 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_54e2a8a6-06af-4d5b-b812-a07814deacd3_500x.png?v=1708696015 320w" width="1187" height="818" alt="Elevating Skills for Tomorrow: The Role of ComplyPlus in Professional Development - Dr Richard Dune - " title="Elevating Skills for Tomorrow: The Role of ComplyPlus in Professional Development - Dr Richard Dune - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-141_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-142_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by mihacreative via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-144_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">In the unstructured environment of play, children often display early signs of business intelligence. The child who organises games negotiates roles among peers, or barter toys demonstrates basic leadership principles, negotiation, and value assessment. These are the nascent stages of skills critical in business – the ability to lead, see opportunity, negotiate, and understand the value of assets.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-146_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-147_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-148_">Teenage years - The testing ground
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_b2a27be0-c4f2-4101-b5fd-f56116bfbb11.png?v=1708696015" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_b2a27be0-c4f2-4101-b5fd-f56116bfbb11.png?v=1708696015 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_b2a27be0-c4f2-4101-b5fd-f56116bfbb11_1000x.png?v=1708696015 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_b2a27be0-c4f2-4101-b5fd-f56116bfbb11_500x.png?v=1708696015 320w" width="1200" height="801" alt="Unlocking Business Brilliance: Key Strategies for Early Entrepreneurs - Dr Richard Dune - " title="Unlocking Business Brilliance: Key Strategies for Early Entrepreneurs - Dr Richard Dune - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-150_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-151_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Rawpixel via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-153_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">As children become teenagers, these skills become more pronounced and sophisticated. The teenager who takes a lead role in group projects shows an interest in economics or entrepreneurship or starts a small venture is displaying a maturation of those early signs. These are the years when potential business acumen starts taking a definitive shape, getting tested and refined through practical experiences.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-155_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-156_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-157_">Identifying and nurturing early business talent
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/5_9a47e986-bf95-4667-9283-7f9e74935f0f.png?v=1708696015" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/5_9a47e986-bf95-4667-9283-7f9e74935f0f.png?v=1708696015 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/5_9a47e986-bf95-4667-9283-7f9e74935f0f_1000x.png?v=1708696015 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/5_9a47e986-bf95-4667-9283-7f9e74935f0f_500x.png?v=1708696015 320w" width="1248" height="914" alt="Transforming Talent into Triumph: How The Mandatory Training Group Shapes Leaders - Dr Richard Dune - " title="Transforming Talent into Triumph: How The Mandatory Training Group Shapes Leaders - Dr Richard Dune - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-159_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-160_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by dvatri via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-162_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-163_"><b>Leadership and  initiative</b> - Children and teenagers who naturally take charge in group situations or show initiative in starting projects demonstrate early leadership qualities. Encouraging these tendencies through leadership opportunities can significantly foster their development.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-165_"><b>Problem-solving skills</b> - An inclination towards solving problems, whether in academic projects or daily life scenarios, is a key indicator of business intelligence. Providing complex, real-world problems to solve can help sharpen these skills.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-167_"><b>Negotiation and persuasion</b> - Youngsters who show an ability to negotiate in play or persuade their peers effectively are honing essential business skills. Role-playing games and debates can be effective ways to cultivate these abilities.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-169_"><b>Financial acumen</b> - An early understanding of money, whether through saving pocket money or running a small school business, is a significant sign. Encouraging this through practical financial education and small-scale entrepreneurship projects can be beneficial.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-171_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-172_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-173_">The role of education in cultivating business brilliance
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/6_bdd220af-9ed9-4406-be82-105a6bb5ef15.png?v=1708696015" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/6_bdd220af-9ed9-4406-be82-105a6bb5ef15.png?v=1708696015 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/6_bdd220af-9ed9-4406-be82-105a6bb5ef15_1000x.png?v=1708696015 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/6_bdd220af-9ed9-4406-be82-105a6bb5ef15_500x.png?v=1708696015 320w" width="1420" height="947" alt="Joining the Community of Future Leaders: Insights from ComplyPlus Users - Dr Richard Dune - " title="Joining the Community of Future Leaders: Insights from ComplyPlus Users - Dr Richard Dune - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-175_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-176_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by drazenphoto via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-178_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">While innate tendencies play a significant role, the nurturing environment of education is critical in shaping these early signs into formidable business skills. Educational systems that incorporate practical business experiences, mentorship, and exposure to real-world business scenarios can significantly impact business intelligence development.

</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-180_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-181_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-182_">The importance of failure and resilience
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/7_0d5792b6-6653-4b0f-b905-d9deeea1cacd.png?v=1708696016" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/7_0d5792b6-6653-4b0f-b905-d9deeea1cacd.png?v=1708696016 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/7_0d5792b6-6653-4b0f-b905-d9deeea1cacd_1000x.png?v=1708696016 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/7_0d5792b6-6653-4b0f-b905-d9deeea1cacd_500x.png?v=1708696016 320w" width="1444" height="964" alt="Experience Cutting-Edge Learning with ComplyPlus LMS: A Comprehensive Review - Dr Richard Dune - " title="Experience Cutting-Edge Learning with ComplyPlus LMS: A Comprehensive Review - Dr Richard Dune - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-184_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-185_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Gajus-Images via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-187_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">An often overlooked aspect of nurturing business intelligence is the role of failure and the development of resilience. Bouncing back from setbacks and learning from failures is as vital as celebrating successes. Providing a safe space where young individuals can take risks, fail, and learn from their experiences is crucial in developing resilient business leaders.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-189_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-190_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-191_">Cultivating emotional intelligence
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/8_dcd0bcf1-87a6-4615-9a89-d0ede3a58345.png?v=1708696015" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/8_dcd0bcf1-87a6-4615-9a89-d0ede3a58345.png?v=1708696015 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/8_dcd0bcf1-87a6-4615-9a89-d0ede3a58345_1500x.png?v=1708696015 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/8_dcd0bcf1-87a6-4615-9a89-d0ede3a58345_1000x.png?v=1708696015 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/8_dcd0bcf1-87a6-4615-9a89-d0ede3a58345_500x.png?v=1708696015 320w" width="1884" height="1264" alt="Getting Certified with The Mandatory Training Group: Your Pathway to Success - Dr Richard Dune - " title="Getting Certified with The Mandatory Training Group: Your Pathway to Success - Dr Richard Dune - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-193_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-194_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by  zoranzeremski via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-196_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Goleman’s concept of business intelligence goes beyond cognitive skills to include emotional intelligence. Recognising and managing emotions, empathising with others, and handling interpersonal relationships judiciously should be nurtured alongside traditional business skills. Activities that foster self-awareness, empathy, and effective communication are vital in this regard.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-198_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-199_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-200_">The continuous journey of learning and adaptation
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/9_547ac2e8-5f7e-4516-813f-747b05e85188.png?v=1708696015" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/9_547ac2e8-5f7e-4516-813f-747b05e85188.png?v=1708696015 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/9_547ac2e8-5f7e-4516-813f-747b05e85188_1500x.png?v=1708696015 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/9_547ac2e8-5f7e-4516-813f-747b05e85188_1000x.png?v=1708696015 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/9_547ac2e8-5f7e-4516-813f-747b05e85188_500x.png?v=1708696015 320w" width="1659" height="1094" alt="Advancing Careers Through Expert Training: The ComplyPlus Advantage - Dr Richard Dune - " title="Advancing Careers Through Expert Training: The ComplyPlus Advantage - Dr Richard Dune - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-202_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-203_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by FoToArtist_1 via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-205_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The development of business intelligence is a continuous journey. The business world is dynamic, and staying adaptable and committed to lifelong learning is critical to mastering business skills. Encouraging a mindset of curiosity, adaptability, and a hunger for learning in young individuals sets the foundation for a lifetime of business development.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-207_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-208_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-209_">Conclusion
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/10_7cca0e01-ed48-409a-aff3-38bdfc4a4385.png?v=1708696015" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/10_7cca0e01-ed48-409a-aff3-38bdfc4a4385.png?v=1708696015 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/10_7cca0e01-ed48-409a-aff3-38bdfc4a4385_1500x.png?v=1708696015 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/10_7cca0e01-ed48-409a-aff3-38bdfc4a4385_1000x.png?v=1708696015 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/10_7cca0e01-ed48-409a-aff3-38bdfc4a4385_500x.png?v=1708696015 320w" width="1766" height="1179" alt="From Smart to Brilliant: Identifying Business IQ in the Making - Dr Richard Dune -" title="From Smart to Brilliant: Identifying Business IQ in the Making - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-211_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-215_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-212_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">When identified and nurtured, the early signs of business brilliance can pave the way for remarkable business acumen. As Goleman suggests, these skills, often rooted in fundamental human interactions and problem-solving, can evolve into sophisticated competencies required in the business world. Educators, parents, and mentors are responsible for recognising, encouraging, and refining these talents, shaping the business leaders of tomorrow. In doing so, we foster individual growth and contribute to a future rich in skilled, emotionally intelligent, and adaptive business minds.
</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-4eaa" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-uojGG hMqLeX pf-217_ pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-ilfuhL bpQaoh"><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-218_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-219_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-220_">Related blog articles</h3><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/blogs" target="_blank" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-dtMgUX gJMWBM pf-222_">View all</a></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-224_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-225_"><img alt="{{ article_560895492165.image.alt }}" loading="eager" width="{{ article_560895492165.image.width }}" height="{{ article_560895492165.image.height }}" src="{% if article_560895492165.image %}
